1
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:37,020
What are you doing?

2
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:39,420
Why did you kidnap her?

3
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:41,200
You assaulted a police officer. That's an extra charge.

4
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,930
Are you trying to get me killed?

5
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,920
She is our last bargaining chip.

6
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:47,080
Without her, you can't get out of here.

7
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:48,340
Then how do I leave now?

8
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:49,560
Tell me.

9
00:01:54,759 --> 00:01:55,820
Your new identity.

10
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:58,560
And all the money you gave me before.

11
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,560
Go abroad.

12
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,400
Start your new life.

13
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:15,020
What about you?

14
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:19,640
I can't leave.

15
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,240
But you can.

16
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:35,600
I want you to come with me.

17
00:02:44,920 --> 00:02:45,780
How old are you?

18
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:48,690
All by yourself.

19
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,760
You need to really smile.

20
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,440
Be well.

21
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:42,400
We finally meet.

22
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,240
Boss.

23
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,860
Two steamed buns to go.

24
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,250
I have it.

25
00:06:59,080 --> 00:06:59,940
This is for you.

26
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,320
Thank you.

27
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,640
We're even now.

28
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:20,360
Remember,

29
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:22,600
none of this has anything to do with you.

30
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:46,770
What are your terms?

31
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,980
Get me a flight out of the country.

32
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:50,080
Send her away.

33
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,530
You want to save her.

34
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:55,770
I killed the person.

35
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:57,920
It has nothing to do with her.

36
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,010
But she ordered you to do it.

37
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:01,320
No one ordered me.

38
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:02,640
I wanted to do it.

39
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,300
You have no motive.

40
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,220
She's the one with the motive.

41
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:09,090
You sure talk a lot of nonsense.

42
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,000
Surrender now.

43
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,970
I advise you to agree to my demands.

44
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:16,320
She is wanted all over the city now.

45
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,280
Even if I wanted to let her go,

46
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:19,610
she wouldn't be able to.

47
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,560
You overestimate your abilities.

48
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:25,800
Qian Yong.

49
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:28,200
It has nothing to do with you.

50
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,409
Don't be impulsive.

51
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,120
Let's talk.

52
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,320
Shen Feng,

53
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:36,679
do you really think I won't kill her?

54
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,280
I advise you

55
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:41,400
to agree to my terms.

56
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,679
Even if she escapes abroad,

57
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:46,610
do you think we can't catch her?

58
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:47,920
Cut the crap.

59
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,800
Do you want me to slit her throat,

60
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,800
or gouge out her eyes?

61
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:12,160
Even if I let her go,

62
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:15,360
you must let me make up a story for my superiors.

63
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:16,840
I did everything.

64
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,320
I killed them too.

65
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:21,320
It has nothing to do with her.

66
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,600
So you killed Lu Yang.

67
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:27,320
Haven't you already issued the wanted poster?

68
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,560
You have no motive.

69
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:32,300
She looks like she has the motive.

70
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,520
He was greedy.

71
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:35,680
I just couldn't stand him.

72
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:36,540
He deserved it.

73
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,610
Lu Yang deserved to die.

74
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:41,480
He didn't scam any money from Mr. Ye.

75
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,820
It's useless to come to me.

76
00:09:45,760 --> 00:09:46,820
Look at this first.

77
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:54,760
You are so brave.

78
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:56,020
I'm short on money.

79
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,160
Lend me some to spend.

80
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,180
So you ordered him to kill Lu Yang.

81
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:02,020
I...

82
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:02,640
Shen Feng.

83
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:04,360
I told you I did everything.

84
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,840
It has nothing to do with her.

85
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,840
Then she must have killed Ye Qiming.

86
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,560
I don't want to talk to you.

87
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:13,760
Show me the evidence.

88
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:14,820
Then we won't talk.

89
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:15,840
I'll speak.

90
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:18,000
See if I'm right.

91
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:21,720
What tricks are you trying to play with me now?

92
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,520
No tricks.

93
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,420
Don't we have to make up a story

94
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:26,970
to submit it?

95
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:28,680
Okay.

96
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,000
Then guess.

97
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,000
Anyway, everything is just a guess.

98
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,800
It can't be counted as evidence.

99
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,240
Actually, for Ye Qiming,

100
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:39,040
you came prepared from the very beginning.

101
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,040
Send him up,

102
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,600
and then slowly eat him away, right?

103
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,330
Is that not allowed?

104
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:48,040
Liu Weishan wanted to win the project in the eastern suburbs.

105
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:50,000
But he needed an independent company

106
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,080
to act as a shield,

107
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:54,280
to help him deal with some unnecessary troubles,

108
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:56,440
such as doing some illegal things.

109
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,760
So from among many companies,

110
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,970
you chose Ye Qiming's company.

111
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,520
Pick a company

112
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:08,930
to cooperate with us on the east suburb project next.

113
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:15,160
Judging from the materials Song Qing provided,

114
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,240
the encrypted document inside

115
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,160
is the real evidence of you and Liu Weishan

116
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:18,960
colluding for money and murder.

117
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:21,220
You didn't dare to touch Ye Qiming

118
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,880
because you thought the USB drive

119
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:24,920
was in his hands.

120
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:27,920
Now you are sure the USB drive is not with him.

121
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,860
And you didn't wait for his trial.

122
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,560
The danger of the USB drive to you

123
00:11:32,560 --> 00:11:33,690
is greatly reduced.

124
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,360
And you didn't know

125
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:37,220
that the USB drive was encrypted.

126
00:11:37,680 --> 00:11:39,320
Even if someone else picked it up,

127
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:40,380
they could only see

128
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,720
the criminal records of you and Ye Qiming.

129
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,050
So you killed Ye Qiming.

130
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,360
With all my calculations,

131
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,120
I never thought

132
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:50,380
the USB drive would be in Xia Lin's hands.

133
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,300
And she was so calm and collected.

134
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:55,200
If it weren't for that business between you and Ye Qiming,

135
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:57,600
he would have gotten the USB drive long ago.

136
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:58,800
But Xia Lin thought

137
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:01,280
this USB drive was leverage against Ye Qiming.

138
00:12:01,280 --> 00:12:03,410
She didn't want Ye Qiming to go to jail.

139
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:04,760
You killed him.

140
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:09,610
Your liver isn't good. Remember to take the hangover pills.

141
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:13,760
How did I kill him?

142
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,240
Was I the one who ran him over?

143
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:16,560
I only gave him cephalosporin.

144
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:18,240
What does his death have to do with me?

145
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,680
Can you guarantee that

146
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,720
Ye Qiming's death has absolutely nothing to do with you?

147
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,680
That you didn't instigate or coerce him?

148
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:23,240
I...

149
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,040
I told you.

150
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:27,760
I did everything. It has nothing to do with her.

151
00:12:27,760 --> 00:12:28,920
Nothing at all.

152
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:31,660
Do you think you are saving her by doing this?

153
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,880
You are harming her.

154
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,240
Ye Qiming just didn't want to die

155
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:38,370
under your control.

156
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:40,380
So he threw himself at the car.

157
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:43,960
I don't want to waste my breath on you anymore.

158
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:46,680
You asked Chen Hao to dispose of Tian Liang's phone, didn't you?

159
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:48,360
Ye Qiming got Kuai to kill him,

160
00:12:48,800 --> 00:12:49,640
sent text messages,

161
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,700
and shifted the blame to Liu Weishan.

162
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:54,200
Liu Weishan doesn't want to deal with us

163
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:56,160
because his own hands are dirty.

164
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:58,200
But why is Ye Qiming

165
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,520
so hostile towards Liu Weishan?

166
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:01,600
Because Ye Qiming is selfish.

167
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:04,560
He wants to use his own people to achieve his goals.

168
00:13:04,560 --> 00:13:05,760
Isn't that obvious?

169
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:08,960
But Liu Weishan also has his own people he wants to promote.

170
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:09,560
Of course.

171
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:10,880
That's human nature.

172
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:13,280
People shouldn't be too greedy.

173
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:18,540
What right do you have to judge me?

174
00:13:19,680 --> 00:13:21,880
Actually, you already have a lot.

175
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,890
But you still feel it's not enough.

176
00:13:26,520 --> 00:13:28,380
In the end, you held onto nothing.

177
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:32,300
I don't want anything.

178
00:13:33,160 --> 00:13:34,400
I just want Ye Qiming dead.

179
00:13:34,400 --> 00:13:35,560
He deserves it.

180
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:39,460
Let go of your grudges.

181
00:13:40,640 --> 00:13:41,480
Start over.

182
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:45,250
Do I really still have a chance?

183
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:47,960
No.

184
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:52,120
Actor
